cdata.desc: Locihas createdInnVenn",a search tool thatdraws from an expansive database provided by inventors directly. The system serves inventors by offering immutable proof of intellectual property rights on a global scale presented inan interactive, user-modifiable, and visually appealing Venn diagram of technologies, inventions, patents and ideas.The LOCI token is an ERC20 token used to pay for services in the InnVenn app, and as a medium of exchange to buy and sell intelectual purpose
